  "description": "The inverse-threshold showcase: xfFloorEmerg is set to -0.55 (negative). In EcosystemMatrix, negative threshold amounts trigger on SILENCE, not on peaks. When the floor goes quiet between beats, creature calls fire. The ecosystem reacts to the rests. A texture that breathes in negative space — the Pandeiro drums fall silent, and then the jungle speaks.",
